{"tid":1123065,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"網上電台 Leisure Radio","createTime":"2019-04-24T09:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T17:29:03.000Z","uid":250047,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b1874f539758621b94de12ce8afe46d5651333d3","tid":1123065,"uid":250047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:02:01.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟近日喺度整理下自己嘅物品<br />\n執執下竟然搵到自己以前自己用過嘅JTV Account <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前開台嘅回憶即刻湧曬出嚟<br />\n突然間好想好似以前咁喺JTV開台<br />\n同大家一齊嘻嘻哈哈過下日晨<br />\n但可惜JTV而家已經連影都無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就喺我想打消返呢個念頭之際<br />\n發現左Discord其實都做到一樣嘅功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至運作上更加流暢<br />\n延遲亦都更加低<br />\n所以我就嗱嗱聲開左個Channel<br />\n命名為 'Leisure Radio 休閒電台'<br />\n顧名思義呢度係一個比大家放低平日重擔嘅平台<br />\n希望大家有興趣都可以賞個面入嚟吹下水一齊放鬆下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家初步估計呢個Channel主要都係用電台嘅方式同大家傾下偈<br />\n未必每一次都有特定嘅主題<br />\n起初呢度可能會更偏向一個吹水平台咁<br />\n而開台期間唔少得嘅當然係Phone-in環節啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會比大家上嚟Share下自己大大小小嘅趣事<br />\n又或者有煩惱都可以喺度同大家傾訴下<br />\n另外我地都會用下Discord嘅Function嚟播下歌又或者播下片咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下送上Discord傳送門︰ <a href=\"https://discord.gg/qzeyzgN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FqzeyzgN&d=olYBpEtcm7PlGpSikb%2Bc0tG7VHCXrvZUts5J42m7pqo%3D&h=34836497\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/qzeyzgN</a><br />\n<br />\n有鑑於小弟嘅工作關係<br />\n做唔到每日都喺固定時間開台<br />\n所以只要決定左幾時會開台就會透過以下渠道Update大家︰<br />\nDiscord: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/qzeyzgN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FqzeyzgN&d=olYBpEtcm7PlGpSikb%2Bc0tG7VHCXrvZUts5J42m7pqo%3D&h=34836497\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/qzeyzgN</a><br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/LeisureRadio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FLeisureRadio&d=olYBpEtcm7PlGpSikb%2Bc0tG7VHCXrvZUts5J42m7pqo%3D&h=0db4c917\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/LeisureRadio</a> <br />\n<br />\n如果大家有咩建議又或者有咩疑問，亦都可以透過上面兩個途徑去直接聯絡我 (Telegram嘅話可以撳呢條Link搵到我：<a href=\"https://t.me/hasumisan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhasumisan&d=olYBpEtcm7PlGpSikb%2Bc0tG7VHCXrvZUts5J42m7pqo%3D&h=1c8fc2b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hasumisan</a>)<br />\n<br />\n平時日頭大家無野做都可以入嚟吹下水<br />\n因為Discord唔係純粹一個語音頻道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦可以當做一個比大家Texting嘅平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後多謝你睇到嚟呢一度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望可以喺Leisure Radio入面見到你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204dbbff46e62ac4f6d7c3a5494ceac90284cb0e","tid":1123065,"uid":250047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T09:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2510227fad5412dab6ed38139e3d585cd454a5d8","tid":1123065,"uid":250047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T10:25:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893f53d91a855cbd98553d966d6fbf26fad9fed9","tid":1123065,"uid":250047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d9fce35d38801784c19fa3247d131cf63ff079","tid":1123065,"uid":250047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T11:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6195aa0e4b62c66be44f37c9ec796479083cd6","tid":1123065,"uid":250047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T12:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"047fc0d5d22f26ae229a60b99ed8